Package: tmT
Type: Package
Title: Text Mining Tools For News Corpora Analysis
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-06-30
Author: Lars Koppers
Maintainer: Lars Koppers <koppers@statistik.tu-dortmund.de>
Description: This package contains three different types of functions: 1. Preprocessing of data. 2. functions for an easy use of latent dirichlet allocation. 3. tools to analyse LDA results.
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyLoad: yes
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0), tm (>= 0.6), lda (>= 1.3.2), lubridate (>= 1.3.3)